snippet.title: Cannon Fodder Amiga game intro
snippet.description:
This is the game introduction for the great game Cannon Fodder for the Amiga computer done by Sensible Software. I find it pretty fun, so I decided to share it.

I was recorded using the WinUAE emulator capture features. Enjoy it :)
